    "map_entry": "Project guide for creating an HTML/JS dashboard that visualizes Thai and global gold price data via APIs, including a CORS proxy example.",
    "summary": "This document explains how to build a lightweight web-based dashboard to compare Thai gold prices with global gold prices. It outlines the folder structure (index.html, dashboard.js, README, optional proxy.php), provides sample code using Chart.js for rendering time‑series charts, and details API endpoints (Thai real‑time data JSON and CoinGecko price). The guide includes steps for handling CORS via a simple PHP proxy, instructions to set up the project locally or on a web server, and notes on extending the UI. It serves as a practical reference for developers looking to prototype real‑time gold price comparisons.",
