    "summary": "The user needs a single, focused pipeline that takes one still image and produces a short animated video. The recommended approach is to load the image into ComfyUI, feed it through the WAN 2.2 Image‑to‑Video node (setting FPS, duration, and model path), and then pipe the output frames into a Video Save/Encode node to write an MP4 file. No additional nodes or enhancements are required. This concise workflow eliminates distractions and ensures reliable video generation on the available GPU.",
